        notes: "A novice at the Citadel in Oldtown. The youngest of the group — a 'chunky boy still two years shy of manhood' (about 14-15 years old). He is naive and asks simple questions. He says he would like to see a dragon. Appears in the Prologue at the Quill and Tankard with Pate, Alleras, Armen, and Mollander. (AFFC Prologue)"
